  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Provides that any person eighteen (18) years of age who is issued a license or permit may carry a stun gun. It would impose criminal penalties for a person to sell or transfer a stun gun to a person under the age of eighteen (18)."
    }
